$ Bitcoin clients

Bitcoin clients are software that enables the use of → development/Crypto-Currencies/Bitcoin[Bitcoin].

There are three types of clients
table { ll
  Full client ☰ Or *full node*: It stores the entire blockchain, manages a user's wallet and is able to initiate a transaction on the bitcoin network. → development/Crypto-Currencies/Bitcoin/clients/Bitcoin-Core is such a client.
  Lightweight client ☰ it stores the user's wallet but relies on 3rd party services for transaction validation and initiation of transactions
  Web client ☰ 
table }

